data.title: Straße 105, 04275 Leipzig, Germany with Panasonic DMC
data.meta_description: The photo was taken using a Panasonic DMC-FT5 camera at Karl-Liebknecht-Straße 105, 04275 Leipzig, Germany.
data.text:
The photo was shot using a Panasonic DMC-FT5 camera at an aperture of f/3.3, 1/800 sec. shutter speed and ISO 160. Flash did not fire, compulsory flash mode. The original image file has a resolution of 4608 x 3456 pixels, or in other words 15.9 megapixels.The photo has a resolution of 180 DPI.

According to the image metadata, the photo was shot on Wednesday 17th of June 2015. The local time was 17:45:23. The timezone was Europe / Berlin, which is GMT +02:00. Please note that timezone was guessed using the GPS coordinates and may not be accurate. The EXIF timestamp may also be wrong if the date and time weren't set correctly in the digital camera.

Panasonic DMC-FT5 camera has a built-in GPS receiver and allows geotagging on image files. The coordinates and location where the photo was taken is stored in the EXIF. According to GPS data analysis, the photo was taken at coordinates 51° 19' 13.01" N , 12° 22' 26.55" E. The elevation was 40 meters. Using reverse geocoding, the address associated with the coordinates is guessed as Karl-Liebknecht-Straße 105, 04275 Leipzig, Germany. Depending on the GPS receiver and the reception conditions the accuracy may vary and the address should not be regarded as exact location.
